name: Made of Ice
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 10

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.3-0.7.

  • Keys: made_of_ice

I made this model just for fun. It works as expected, it just makes the subject made of ice like a ice statue (it has been trained on ice statue artworks)

I have tryied to use it with other LoRAs, like clothing LoRAs and it usually doesn't work.

The training images are not only about humans, there are many about animals and fantasy stuff, so it should be able to generate a statue of everything, just give it a try maybe with a xy plot on the weights.

Doesn't give it's best with humans, but with a lucky seed this model can manage to generate a good ice human statue.

Look at images prompts to have something to start with.

It should work also with anime.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
